{"tid":227813,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"我隻龜唔見左，巴絲有無咩方法引佢出黎？","createTime":"2017-05-03T12:43:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T17:11:26.000Z","uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bd79b3dc83a4a0d5e54ae98161aa264a9af69892","tid":227813,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T12:43:02.000Z","msg":"話說今日瞓醒 發現隻龜唔係個箱到 我知佢平時都爬到出黎 但我都可以依附近搵得返 但今次搵晒成屋都唔見 我唔知佢係邊 但我肯定佢係間屋入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無巴絲有計仔引佢出黎 事關我間屋唔係好大架咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我隻龜仔就我手掌心咁大 養左7 8年啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaee3caab2eaeb7615d2a5d46d40f1930d6f1c55","tid":227813,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T13:24:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf536bf4e00178fe40a0a0abe0aad547d584f8a5","tid":227813,"uid":77134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T13:25:57.000Z","msg":"結印"},{"pid":"0fe33975831ba1ecfc990aa76b04a2a9ddd43b01","tid":227813,"uid":1394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T13:27:08.000Z","msg":"留意下門之間"},{"pid":"1c561ef830dddac59cccd16a95e680d3229d863c","tid":227813,"uid":37636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T13:35:39.000Z","msg":"再搵多次間屋啦～<br />\n留意下啲櫃底床底之類嘅暗位，佢地好鐘意爬去嗰度<br />\n我兩隻龜次次走甩我都知佢爬去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"011a21ed7c32f617ae8d668b58ebec39367b8e38","tid":227813,"uid":38146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T13:45:48.000Z","msg":"我隻龜試過爬左去馬桶後面個lon入面  你可以去睇下有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e9e2d227e5f8c5db66dee6cbbc4dfab69ba285","tid":227813,"uid":62473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T15:34:40.000Z","msg":"我仲試過雪櫃底 要成家人抬起<br />\n同埋試過煤氣錶櫃位"},{"pid":"8c854a